      <title>韩国议会在关键选举前通过预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/south-korean-parliament-passes-budget-ahead-of-crucial-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国议会批准了明年 656.6 万亿韩元（5030 亿美元）的预算，结束了 4 月份选举前的谈判，选举可能决定总统尹锡烈 (Yoon Suk Yeol) 剩余任期的统治有效性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/south-korean-parliament-passes-budget-ahead-of-crucial-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 07:38:42 GMT</pubDate>
